'[[#ref A|^]]''' \"Who Will Save Your Soul\" peaked at No. 14 on the Canadian ''RPM'' Rock Singles chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-110.01-e.php?PHPSESSID=ujkbpqflduvhi8o2iaadcla7v3&q1=Jewel&q2=Rock%2FAlternative&interval=20|title=Results - RPM - Library and Archives Canada - Rock/Alternative|work=[[RPM (magazine)|RPM]]|accessdate=November 2, 2010}}</ref>\n*B<span id=\"endnote_B\"></span>'''[[#ref B|^]]''' \"Again and Again\" was released as a double A-side single with \"Goodbye Alice in Wonderland\" in some countries.\n{{refend}}\n\n==Miscellaneous==\n\n===Tributes===\n*\"You Make Loving Fun\" (''Legacy: A Tribute to [[Fleetwood Mac]]'s [[Rumours (album)|Rumours]]'')\n*\"Body On Body\" (''[[Forever Words|Johnny Cash: Forever Words]]'')\n\n===Soundtracks===\n*\"All By Myself\" (''[[Clueless (film)|Clueless]]'' OST - Unreleased-Not available on soundtrack CD)\n*\"Emily\"  (''[[The Crossing Guard]]'' OST)\n*\"Sunshine Superman\" (''[[I Shot Andy Warhol]]'' OST)\n*\"Under the Water\" (''[[The Craft (film)|The Craft]]'' OST)\n*\"[[Have a Little Faith in Me]]\" (''[[Phenomenon (film)|Phenomenon]]'' OST)\n*\"Foolish Games (radio mix version)\" (''[[Batman & Robin (film)|Batman & Robin]]'' OST)\n*\"What's Simple Is True\" (''[[Ride with the Devil (film)|Ride with the Devil]]'' OST)\n*\"Angel Standing By\"  (\"[[Return to Me]]\" OST)\n*\"Sweet Home Alabama\" (''[[Sweet Home Alabama (film)|Sweet Home Alabama]]'' OST)\n*\"Quest for Love\" (''[[Arthur and the Invisibles]]'' OST)\n*\"[[Stay Here Forever]]\" (''[[Valentine's Day (2010 film)|Valentine's Day]]'' OST)\n*\"Alaska: The Last Frontier Theme Song (Acoustic)\" (''[[Alaska: The Last Frontier|Alaska: The Last Frontier - The Soundtrack]]'')\n\n=== EP promos ===\n* 1994: ''Save the Linoleum'' (promo)\n* 1994: ''Shiva Diva Doo-Wop'' (promo)\n* 1995: ''You Were Meant for Me'' aka ''Phyllis Barnabee Finally Gets a Bra'' (promo PRCD 6416-2)\n* 1999: ''Bits and Baubles'' (promo)\n\n==Music v